Object.watch 

  void watch ( <L=51#6> String </L> name , <L=2M#5> Function </L> func )

Parameters 

  ------------- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  name          The name of the property to watch.

  func          The function to be called when the value of this property changes.
  ------------- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Adds a watch function to a property, which is called when the value changes.

This function can accept, modify, or reject a new value that the user, application, or a script has
attempted to place in a property.
<I=3>
</B>
