RegExp.exec 

  <L=4#5> Array </L> exec ( <L=51#6> String </L> text )

Parameters 

  -------------------------------- -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  text                             The string to match.

  -------------------------------- -----------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Execute a regular expression.

The return value is an array of matches, with the first element containing the match, and successive
elements containing the results of any matching subexpression in their order of appearance. If there is
no match, the result is null.
