  limit                      
  -------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Splits a string into a group of substrings, places those strings in an array, and returns the array.

The substrings are created by breaking the original string at places that match delimiter, the delimiter
characters are removed. Returns an array whose elements are the substrings.
