UnitValue 

Description 

Represents a measurement as a combination of values and unit.

Note that this object is not available in all applications.

Properties 

  ------------------------------------------------------------------------ -------------------------------
  <L=5G#2> baseUnit </L> readonly                                          The base unit.

  <L=5I#2> type </L> readonly                                              The unit name.

  <L=5J#2> value </L> readonly                                             The numeric value.
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------ -------------------------------

Static Properties 

  ---------------------------------------------------------- ---------------------------------------------
  <L=5G#2> baseUnit </L> readonly                            The base unit for all conversions.

  ---------------------------------------------------------- ---------------------------------------------

Methods 

