  <L=5K#6> XML </L> appendChild ( <L=5K#6> XML </L> child )

Parameters 

  --------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------
  child                             The child XML to add.

  --------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Appends the given XML to this XML as a child. Returns the XML object itself.

If the argument is not XML, creates a new XML element containing the argument as text. The element name
of that new XML is the same as the last element in the original XML.
