global.encodeURI 

  <L=51#6> String </L> encodeURI ( <L=51#6> String </L> text )

Parameters 

  --------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------
  text                              The text to encode.

  --------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Encodes a string after RFC2396.

Create an UTF-8 ASCII encoded version of this string. The string is converted into UTF-8. Every
non-alphanumeric character is encoded as a percent escape character of the form %xx, where xx is the hex
value of the character. After the conversion to UTF-8 encoding and escaping, it is guaranteed that the
string does not contain characters codes greater than 127. The list of characters not to be encoded is
-_.!~*’();/?:@&=+$,#. The method returns false on errors.
<I=3>
</B>
=========================================================================================================
