  -------------- -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Extracts a floating-point number from a string.

Parses a string to find the first set of characters that can be converted to a floating point number, and
returns that number, or NaN if it does not encounter characters that it can converted to a number. The
function supports exponential notation.
