ActionDescriptor 

Description 

A record of key-value pairs for actions, such as those included on the Adobe Photoshop Actions menu. The
ActionDescriptor class is part of the Action Manager functionality. For more details on the Action
Manager, see the Photoshop Scripting Guide.

