AntiAlias 

Description 

The method to use to smooth edges by softening the color transition between edge pixels and background
pixels.

Static Properties 

  --------------------------------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------
  <L=7I#2> CRISP </L> readonly                              Makes type appear somewhat sharp.

  <L=7J#2> NONE </L> readonly                               Does not use anti-aliasing.

  <L=7K#2> SHARP </L> readonly                              Makes type appear its sharpest.

  <L=7L#2> SMOOTH </L> readonly                             Makes type appear smoother.

  <L=7M#2> STRONG </L> readonly                             Makes type appear heavier.
  --------------------------------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------
</B>
=========================================================================================================
