Application.batch 

  <L=51#6> String </L> batch ( AliasArray inputFiles , <L=51#6> String </L> action , <L=51#6> String </L>
  from , BatchOptions options )

Parameters 

  ------------ ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  inputFiles   The files to operate on.

  action       The name of the action to play (note that the Action name is case-sensitive and must match the
               name in the Actions palette).

  from         The name of the action set containing the action being played (note that the Action Set name
               is case-sensitive and must match the name in the Actions palette).

  options      Options for batch automation.
  ------------ ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Runs the batch automation routine; analogous to using the Batch command in Photoshop.
