ArtLayer.applyCustomFilter 

  void applyCustomFilter (int characteristics , int scale , int offset )

Parameters 

  ----------------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  characteristics   The custom filter characteristics. This is an array of 25 values that corresponds to a
                    left-to-right, top-to- bottom traversal of the array presented in the Custom dialog in the
                    user interface (Filter > Other > Custom).

