ArtLayer.threshold 

  void threshold (int level )

Parameters 

  ---------------------------------- ---------------------------------------------------------------------
  level                              The threshold level.

  ---------------------------------- ---------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Converts grayscale or color images to high-contrast, B/W images by converting pixels lighter than the
specified threshold to white and pixels darker than the threshold to black.
