AutoKernType 

Description 

The type of kerning to use for characters.

Static Properties 

  ----------------------------------- --------------------------------------------------------------------
  <L=ak#2> MANUAL </L> readonly       Allows manual kerning.

  <L=al#2> METRICS </L> readonly      Uses kern pairs, which contain information about the spacing of
                                      specific pairs of letters.

  <L=am#2> OPTICAL </L> readonly      Adjusts the spacing between adjacent characters based on their
                                      shapes.
  ----------------------------------- --------------------------------------------------------------------
</B>
