BitmapConversionType.CUSTOMPATTERN 

  int CUSTOMPATTERN

Description 

Simulates the effect of printing a grayscale image through a custom halftone screen. This method lets you
apply a screen texture, such as a wood grain, to an image. To use this option, you must first define a
pattern.
<I=2>
</B>
