BlendMode.LINEARLIGHT 

  int LINEARLIGHT

Description 

Burns or dodges the colors by decreasing or increasing the brightness, depending on the blend color. If
the blend color (light source) is lighter than 50% gray, the image is lightened by increasing the
brightness. If the blend color is darker than 50% gray, the image is darkened by decreasing the
brightness.
<I=2>
</B>
