BlendMode.PASSTHROUGH 

  int PASSTHROUGH

Description 

Allows any blend modes, advanced blending options, and opacity and fill values applied to layers within a
set to affect layers below the set in the Layers palette.

Valid only for layer sets. To restrict blend modes of the layers within a set, change the layer set’s
blend mode to Normal.
<I=2>
</B>
