BlendMode.PINLIGHT 

  int PINLIGHT

Description 

Replaces the colors, depending on the blend color. If the blend color (light source) is lighter than 50%
gray, pixels darker than the blend color are replaced, and pixels lighter than the blend color do not
change. If the blend color is darker than 50% gray, pixels lighter than the blend color are replaced, and
pixels darker than the blend color do not change. This is useful for adding special effects to an image.
<I=2>
</B>
