BlendMode.SCREEN 

  int SCREEN

Description 

Looks at each channel?s color information and multiplies the inverse of the blend and base colors. The
result color is always a lighter color. Screening with black leaves the color unchanged. Screening with
white produces white. The effect is similar to projecting multiple photographic slides on top of each
other.
<I=2>
</B>
=========================================================================================================
