CameraRAWOpenOptions 

Description 

Options for opening a camera RAW document.

Static Properties 

  ----------------------------------------------------------- --------------------------------------------
  <L=c0#2> bitsPerChannel </L> readonly                       The number of bits per channel.

  <L=c1#2> blueHue </L> readonly                              The blue hue of the shot. Range: -100 to
                                                              100.

