                                                              to 100.

  <L=c3#2> brightness </L> readonly                           The brightness of the shot. Range: 0 to 150.

  <L=c4#2> chromaticAberrationBY </L> readonly                The chromatic aberration B/Y of the shot.
                                                              Range: -100 to 100.

  <L=c5#2> chromaticAberrationRC </L> readonly                The chromatic aberration R/C of the shot.
                                                              Range: -100 to 100.

  <L=c6#2> colorNoiseReduction </L> readonly                  The color noise reduction of the shot.
