ColorBlendMode.COLOR 

  int COLOR

Description 

Creates a result color with the luminance of the base color and the hue and saturation of the blend
color. This preserves the gray levels in the image and is useful for coloring monochrome images and for
tinting color images.
<I=2>
</B>
