ColorBlendMode.DIFFERENCE 

  int DIFFERENCE

Description 

Looks at the color information in each channel and subtracts either the blend color from the base color
or the base color from the blend color, depending on which has the greater brightness value. Blending
with white inverts the base color values; blending with black produces no change.
<I=2>
</B>
