ColorBlendMode.OVERLAY 

  int OVERLAY

Description 

Multiplies or screens the colors, depending on the base color. Patterns or colors overlay the existing
pixels while preserving the highlights and shadows of the base color. The base color is not replaced but
is mixed with the blend color to reflect the lightness or darkness of the original color.
<I=2>
</B>
=========================================================================================================
