ColorBlendMode.SOFTLIGHT 

  int SOFTLIGHT

Description 

Darkens or lightens the colors, depending on the blend color. The effect is similar to shining a diffused
spotlight on the image. If the blend color (light source) is lighter than 50% gray, the image is
lightened as if it were dodged. If the blend color is darker than 50% gray, the image is darkened as if
it were burned in. Painting with pure black or white produces a distinctly darker or lighter area but
does not result in pure black or white.
<I=2>
</B>
=========================================================================================================
