ColorBlendMode.VIVIDLIGHT 

  int VIVIDLIGHT

Description 

Burns or dodges the colors by increasing or decreasing the contrast, depending on the blend color. If the
blend color (light source) is lighter than 50% gray, the image is lightened by decreasing the contrast.
If the blend color is darker than 50% gray, the image is darkened by increasing the contrast.
<I=2>
</B>
