DitherType 

Description 

The type of dither.

Static Properties 

  ------------------------------ -------------------------------------------------------------------------
  <L=gb#2> DIFFUSION </L>        Diffuses dither effects in random patterns across adjacent pixels.
  readonly                       

  <L=gc#2> NOISE </L> readonly   Applies a random pattern but without diffusing the pattern across
                                 adjacent pixels; prevents the appearance of seams.

  <L=gd#2> NONE </L> readonly    No dither is used.

  <L=ge#2> PATTERN </L> readonly Applies a halftone-like square pattern.
