Intent.PERCEPTUAL 

  int PERCEPTUAL

Description 

Gives priority to colors for which the human eye has greater sensitivity.

Suitable for photographic images with a lot of out of gamut colors. This is the standard rendering intent
for the Japanese printing industry.
<I=2>
</B>
