Justification 

Description 

The placement of paragraph text within the bounding box.

Static Properties 

  -------------------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------------------
  <L=no#2> CENTER </L> readonly                      Text is centered on each line.

  <L=np#2> CENTERJUSTIFIED </L> readonly             Justifies all lines except the last, which is
                                                     center-aligned.

  <L=nq#2> FULLYJUSTIFIED </L> readonly              Justifies all lines including the last, which is
                                                     force-justified.

