  <L=oK#2> length </L> readonly                            Number of elements in the collection.

  <L=oL#2> parent </L> readonly                            The object’s container.

  <L=oN#2> typename </L> readonly                          The class name of the object.
  -------------------------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------------

Methods 

  ------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------
  [] readonly                                 Get an element in the collection with the provided index.

  <L=oI#2> add </L> readonly                  Adds an element.

  <L=oJ#3> getByName </L> readonly            Get the first element in the collection with the provided
