  -------------------------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------------

Methods 

  ------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------
  [] readonly                                 Get an element in the collection with the provided index.

  <L=qo#3> getByName </L> readonly            Get the first element in the collection with the provided
                                              name.
