PaletteType.LOCALADAPTIVE 

  int LOCALADAPTIVE

Description 

Creates a palette by sampling the colors from the spectrum appearing most commonly in the image.

For example, an RGB image with only the colors green and blue produces a palette made primarily of greens
and blues.
<I=2>
</B>
