PaletteType.WEBPALETTE 

  int WEBPALETTE

Description 

The 216-color palette that web browsers, regardless of platform, use to display images on a monitor
limited to 256 colors.

A subset of the Mac OS 8-bit palette. Use this option to avoid browser dither when viewing images on a
monitor display limited to 256 colors.
<I=2>
</B>
