PicturePackageOptions 

Description 

Options that can be specified for a Picture Package.

Static Properties 

  ------------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------
  <L=uo#2> content </L> readonly                    The content information.

  <L=up#2> flatten </L> readonly                    If true, flattens all layers in the final document.

  <L=uq#2> font </L> readonly                       The font used for security text.

  <L=ur#2> fontSize </L> readonly                   The font size.

  <L=us#2> layout </L> readonly                     The layout to use to generate the picture package.

  <L=ut#2> mode </L> readonly                       The document color mode.

  <L=uu#2> opacity </L> readonly                    The web page security text opacity (as a percentage)
                                                    Range: 0 to 100.

  <L=uv#2> resolution </L> readonly                 The resolution of the document (in pixels per inch)

  <L=uw#2> text </L> readonly                       The picture package custom text.

  <L=ux#2> textColor </L> readonly                  The color of the security text.

  <L=uy#2> textPosition </L> readonly               The position of the security text.

  <L=uz#2> textRotate </L> readonly                 The orientation of the security text.
  ------------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------
</B>
