RasterizeType 

Description 

The type of the layer content to rasterize.

Static Properties 

  -------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------
  <L=wn#2> ENTIRELAYER </L> readonly           Rasterizes all vector data on the layer.

  <L=wo#2> FILLCONTENT </L> readonly           Rasterizes the fill of a shape layer, leaving the vector
                                               mask.

  <L=wp#2> LAYERCLIPPINGPATH </L> readonly     Rasterizes the vector mask of a shape layer, turning it into
                                               a layer mask.

  <L=wq#2> LINKEDLAYERS </L> readonly          Rasterizes the selected layers.

  <L=wr#2> SHAPE </L> readonly                 Rasterizes a shape layer.

  <L=ws#2> TEXTCONTENTS </L> readonly          Rasterizes the type on a type layer. Doesn’t rasterize any
                                               other vector data on the layer.
  -------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------
</B>
