ResampleMethod.BICUBIC 

  int BICUBIC

Description 

Uses a weighted average to determine pixel color, which usually yields better results than the simple
averageing method of downsampling.

The slowest but most precise method, resulting in the smoothest gradations.
<I=2>
</B>
