ResampleMethod.NEARESTNEIGHBOR 

  int NEARESTNEIGHBOR

Description 

Chooses a pixel in the center of the sample area and replaces the entire area with that pixel color. Same
as subsampling.

Significantly reduces the conversion time compared with downsampling but results in images that are less
smooth and continuous.
<I=2>
</B>
=========================================================================================================
