  ------------------------------------ -------------------------------------------------------------------
  <L=y6#2> DIMINISH </L> readonly      Remove the selection from the already selected area.

  <L=y7#2> EXTEND </L> readonly        Add the selection to an already selected area.

  <L=y8#2> INTERSECT </L> readonly     Make the selection only the area where the new selection intersects
                                       the already selected area.

  <L=y9#2> REPLACE </L> readonly       Replace the selected area.
