ShapeOperation 

Description 

Specifies how to combine the shapes if the destination image already has a selection.

Static Properties 

  ----------------------------------------------- --------------------------------------------------------
  <L=yE#2> SHAPEADD </L> readonly                 Adds the shapes.

  <L=yF#2> SHAPEINTERSECT </L> readonly           The resulting shape is the area of intersection between
                                                  the two shapes.

  <L=yG#2> SHAPESUBTRACT </L> readonly            Subtracts the loaded shape from the selection is the
                                                  destination image.

  <L=yH#2> SHAPEXOR </L> readonly                 Replaces the shape in the destination image with the
                                                  loaded selection.
  ----------------------------------------------- --------------------------------------------------------
</B>
