TrimType 

Description 

The type of pixels to trim around an image.

Static Properties 

  -------------------------------- -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  <L=BU#2> BOTTOMRIGHT </L>        Removes from the image an area the color of the lower right pixel.
  readonly                         

  <L=BV#2> TOPLEFT </L> readonly   Removes from the image an area the color of the upper left pixel.

  <L=BW#2> TRANSPARENT </L>        Trims away transparency at the edges of the image, leaving the smallest
