Events.createEvent 

  Event createEvent ( <L=51#6> String </L> eventType )

Parameters 

  ---------------- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  eventType        The name of an event type: one of “UIEvent”, “KeyboardEvent”, or “MouseEvent”.

  ---------------- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Creates an instance of the specified?Event?subclass.

The?Event?returned is a?UIEvent, KeyboardEvent?or?MouseEvent?object, depending on the requested type.
This object can be passed as a parameter to an element’s dispatchEvent function in order to simulate a
user-interaction event.
