ListItem.subItems 

  <L=4#5> Array </L> subItems

Description 

When the parent is a multi-column?ListBox, this describes the labels for this selectable row in
additional columns.

A array of JavaScript objects whose length is one less than the number of columns. The first member
describes the label in the second column. Each member object has two properties, of which you can specify
one or both: text: A display string for the corresponding label. image: An?ScriptUIImage?object for the
corresponding label.
