ListItem.type 

  <L=51#6> String </L> type

Description 

The element type.

Normally “item”, but an item whose parent is a?DropDownList?control can have type “separator”. A
separator item is not mouse-sensitive and is drawn as a horizontal line across the drop-down or pop-up
menu.
