Panel.layout 

  LayoutManager layout

Description 

The layout manager for this container.

The first time a container object is made visible, ScriptUI invokes this layout manager by calling
its?layout()?function. Default is an instance of the?LayoutManager?class that is automatically created
when the container element is created.
