  <L=Ju#2> hide </L> readonly                    Hides this element.

  <L=JF#3> removeEventListener </L> readonly     Unregisters an event handler for a particular type of
                                                 event occuring in this element.

  <L=JG#2> show </L> readonly                    Shows this element.
