Progressbar.onDraw 

  void onDraw ()

Description 

An event-handler callback function, called when the window is about to be drawn.

Allows the script to modify or control the appearance, using the control?s
associated?ScriptUIGraphics?object. Handler takes one argument, a?DrawState?object.
