Progressbar.properties 

  <L=3F#6> Object </L> properties

Description 

An object that contains one or more creation properties of the container (properties used only when the
element is created).

A ProgressBar object has no creation properties. The third argument of the?add()?method that creates it
is the initial value (default 0), and the fourth argument is the maximum value of the range (default
100).
