ScriptUIBrush.color 

  <L=3r#5> Number </L> color

Description 

The brush color.

The paint color to use when the type is SOLID_COLOR. An array in the form [R, B, G, A] specifying the
red, green, blue values of the color and the opacity (alpha channel) value as numbers in the range
[0.0..1.0]. An opacity of 0 is fully transparent, and an opacity of 1 is fully opaque.
<I=2>
</B>
