ScriptUIGraphics.disabledBackgroundColor 

  ScriptUIBrush disabledBackgroundColor

Description 

The background color for containers when disabled or inactive; for non-containers, the parent background
color.

The paint color and style is defined in this brush object.This property is only supported for controls
like dropdownlist, edittext, and listbox.
