ScriptUIPath 

Description 

A helper object that encapsulates a drawing path for a figure to be drawn into a window or control.

Create with the?newPath(),?moveto(),?lineto(),?rectPath(), and?ellipsePath()?methods. Used as value
of?currentPath, where it is acted upon by methods such as?closePath(). Pass as optional argument
to?fillPath()?and?strokePath(), which otherwise act upon the current path.
</B>
=========================================================================================================
