Window.active 

  Boolean active

Description 

Set to true to make this window active.

A modal dialog that is visible is by definition the active dialog. An active palette is the front-most
window. An active control is the one with focus?that is, the one that accepts keystrokes, or in the case
of a?Button, be selected when the user types Return or Enter.
<I=2>
</B>
