Window.cancelElement 

  <L=3F#6> Object </L> cancelElement

Description 

For windows of type dialog, the UI element to notify when the user presses a cancellation key
combination.

The cancellation key is the Esc key. By default, looks for a button whose name or text is “cancel” (case
disregarded).
<I=2>
</B>
