Window.margins 

  <L=3r#5> Number </L> margins

Description 

The number of pixels between the edges of a container and the outermost child elements.

You can specify different margins for each edge of the container. The default value is based on the type
of container, and is chosen to match the standard Adobe UI guidelines.
