Window.opacity 

  <L=3r#5> Number </L> opacity

Description 

The opacity of the window, in the range [0..1].

A value of 1.0 (the default) makes the window completely opaque, a value of 0 makes it completely
transparent. Intermediate values make it partially transparent to any degree.
