Photoshop Scripting & Extension Reference 

The primary goal of this site was to combine all resources related to scripting and extending Photoshop.
There are many resources if you know where to look, but getting the big picture is sometimes difficult.
Anyhow, hopefully this will shed some light on this love-hate relationship.

-   <L=P2>Photoshop Scripting Documentation</L>
    -   <L=6S>Core</L>
    -   <L=D3>Photoshop</L>
    -   <L=OX>Scriptui</L>
